commit.message:
Add back TsanOopMapTableKey copy constructor to avoid compiler warning:

tsanOopMapTable.hpp:48:23: warning: definition of implicit copy constructor for 'TsanOopMapTableKey' is deprecated because it has a user-declared copy assignment operator [-Wdeprecated-copy]
  TsanOopMapTableKey& operator=(const TsanOopMapTableKey&) = delete;
                      ^
/usr/local/google/home/jianglizhou/github/tsan-oopMap-weakhandle/src/hotspot/share/utilities/resourceHash.hpp:45:18: note: in implicit copy constructor for 'TsanOopMapTableKey' first required here
    _hash(hash), _key(key), _value(value), _next(next) {}
